1. 553 mail from must authorized user
    解决：发送方（from属性）的邮箱格式要与smtp授权的邮箱格式一致，即邮箱@后面的字段相同

2. Cannot create property 'mailer' on string 'SMTP'
    下列代码会引发这种错误
        var mailTransport = nodemailer.createTransport('SMTP',{
            service: 'qq',
            auth: {
                user: credentials.qq.user,
                pass: credentials.qq.password,
            }
        });
    解决：将'SMTP'去掉就不报错
